<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 15:14:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>倍耐力董事会中化高管可能违反意大利规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sinochem-executives-pirelli-board-may-be-breach-italian-rules-2024-11-08/</link><description>一位高级政府官员表示，意大利正在检查中化集团高管在倍耐力董事会的存在是否违反了罗马为保护这家轮胎制造商自主权而实施的措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sinochem-executives-pirelli-board-may-be-breach-italian-rules-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>跑者冒着严寒参加南极超耐力赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/runners-brave-freezing-temperatures-compete-antarctica-ultra-endurance-race-2024-11-08/</link><description>15 名参赛者冒着南极洲的严寒参加了一场史无前例的超耐力比赛，比赛于周四在 Ultima 大本营周围开始，那里的气温低至 -25°C（-13°F）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 13:42:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/runners-brave-freezing-temperatures-compete-antarctica-ultra-endurance-race-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>住宅建筑商困境和中国刺激措施乏善可陈，拖累富时 100 指数跌至 3 个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/homebuilder-woes-lacklustre-china-stimulus-drag-ftse-100-3-month-low-2024-11-08/</link><description>英国富时 100 指数周五跌至三个月低点，原因是房屋建筑商 Vistry 发出盈利预警，而中国刺激措施乏善可陈，打压了投资者情绪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 13:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/homebuilder-woes-lacklustre-china-stimulus-drag-ftse-100-3-month-low-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国最新刺激措施未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</link><description>周五，投资者希望中国宣布为唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统的经济提供额外的财政缓冲，但他们感到失望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国就沃尔沃电动汽车关税协议进行谈判后，瑞典将目光转向布鲁塞尔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sweden-looks-brussels-after-china-talks-volvo-ev-tariff-deal-2024-11-08/</link><description>瑞典外交部长在结束对中国的访问时告诉路透社，瑞典希望欧盟和中国能够尽快就电动汽车达成定价协议，以试图限制进口关税争端对沃尔沃的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:48:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sweden-looks-brussels-after-china-talks-volvo-ev-tariff-deal-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>尽管金价高企，卡地亚所有者历峰集团仍对提高珠宝价格持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-remains-cautious-raising-jewellery-prices-despite-high-gold-prices-2024-11-08/</link><description>高管们周五表示，尽管近几个月金价飙升，卡地亚母公司历峰集团仍计划坚持谨慎提高珠宝价格，并且尚未有在未来几个月提价的计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-remains-cautious-raising-jewellery-prices-despite-high-gold-prices-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：大选后华尔街因美联储降息和中国刺激而繁荣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，台积电将从周一开始暂停为中国生产先进人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tsmc-suspend-production-advanced-ai-chips-china-monday-ft-reports-2024-11-08/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》援引三名知情人士的消息报道，台积电已通知中国芯片设计公司，从周一开始暂停生产最先进的人工智能芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tsmc-suspend-production-advanced-ai-chips-china-monday-ft-reports-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>印度大米库存创历史新高，是政府目标的三倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-rice-inventories-hit-record-high-triples-govt-target-2024-11-08/</link><description>消息人士周五称，由于过去两年实施的出口限制增加了当地供应，印度11月份大米库存飙升至2970万吨的历史新高，几乎是政府目标的三倍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-rice-inventories-hit-record-high-triples-govt-target-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>分析师对中国提高地方政府债务上限的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国最高立法机构周五批准了一项法案，允许地方政府在三年内发行6万亿元人民币（合8,388亿美元）的债券，以置换表外或“隐性”债务，因为政策制定者试图刺激低迷的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>结交新朋友并增加招聘：中国芯片行业计划如何应对特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/make-new-friends-boost-hiring-how-chinas-chip-industry-plans-deal-with-trump-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国半导体行业正准备在唐纳德·特朗普担任美国总统期间迎接四年的激烈竞争，加大对外国芯片制造设备的采购力度，寻找聘用海外人才和建立新联盟的机会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:12:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/make-new-friends-boost-hiring-how-chinas-chip-industry-plans-deal-with-trump-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾被排除在气候峰会之外，设立“作战室”观看会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-excluded-climate-summit-sets-up-war-room-watch-talks-2024-11-08/</link><description>环境部长彭志明周五表示，鉴于台湾因政治原因不能参加，台湾已设立一个“作战室”来观看下周 COP29 气候峰会的直播。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:56:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-excluded-climate-summit-sets-up-war-room-watch-talks-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国钢铁制造商面临特朗普间接关税打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-steelmakers-gird-indirect-trump-tariffs-hit-2024-11-08/</link><description>如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品（例如由合金制成的制成品）征收60％的关税，已经在产能过剩和内需疲软中挣扎的中国钢铁业将面临间接打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:14:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-steelmakers-gird-indirect-trump-tariffs-hit-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>东南亚为逃离特朗普对中国关税的工厂做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</link><description>该地区工业园区开发商表示，企业一直在将工厂从中国迁往东南亚，预计唐纳德·特朗普如果重新入主白宫，将对北京征收高额关税，随着他赢得大选，这一举措将加速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国派副总理出席巴库COP29气候峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</link><description>外交部发言人周五表示，中国副总理丁薛祥将于下周前往阿塞拜疆首都巴库出席第二十九届联合国气候变化框架公约(COP29)峰会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>